{"tid":722573,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拉莫斯滋擾女同學並射殺報館職員","createTime":"2018-06-29T15:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T06:52:02.000Z","uid":34571,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3d1ee3b1ccd6de75d5107c1a0edca8b99223f243","tid":722573,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T15:31:55.000Z","msg":"拉莫斯於自2010年初前後，在社交網站Facebook私訊當時在銀行任職的前高中女同學。他指對方在高中時是唯一對自己友善的人，並就此感謝她。惟女方並不記得拉莫斯，但因有感他受困擾，向他推薦心理輔導。雙方以電郵對話一段時間後，女方認為拉莫斯誤會雙方關係而疏遠他，後更因不堪其擾，要求斷絕來往。<br />\n<br />\n這使拉莫斯勃然大怒，開始辱罵她，循不同途徑滋擾及侵犯女事主的私隱。他甚至向對方任職的公司發電郵希望使其失業，更叫對方自殺。女事主報警，但拉莫斯的行為只停止數月又故態復萌。事件終在2011年鬧上法庭，拉莫斯刑事滋擾罪名成立，判監90日，緩刑18個月，並禁止再接近女事主。<br />\n<br />\n判刑5日後，《首府憲報》針對此案，刊登了一篇以《拉莫斯想跟你做朋友》為題的文章。文中以女事主視角講述案情，描述她遭拉莫斯滋擾而面對的困境及不安。該文借拉莫斯一案引申指出社交網站的危險性。<br />\n<br />\n拉莫斯不滿報道，於2012年兩度入稟控告該文作者哈特利及編輯馬夸特誹謗。法官指出報道內容並無失實，拉莫斯沒否認；惟他指該文章沒有標明內容來源，又稱：「這不公平。」案件終遭法院駁回，上訴亦被拒絕。訴諸法律無果後，他將不忿轉移到網上，一連串事件或為今次槍擊案埋下伏線。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180629/photo/bknint-20180629095654268-0629_17011_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180629%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180629095654268-0629_17011_001_01p.jpg&h=0bc770e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7120966bbbd3f40475ea2c53e561655229c57fb","tid":722573,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T15:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da851ff538a381420ad306b70089fe3a1a35c449","tid":722573,"uid":36716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T15:48:57.000Z","msg":"人如其名"},{"pid":"c04d19bcf9bb15e19dd2e51047de5c0e83286ebe","tid":722573,"uid":25754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T16:01:44.000Z","msg":"應該告唔入啦 佢係莫斯科有不在場證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/spain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/spain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ef094220bfc9a9003589a9f83b501022eba348","tid":722573,"uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T00:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04f95ac6498ef8ca5617ee956618b19b68e3e90","tid":722573,"uid":15376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T00:42:07.000Z","msg":"哇 正賤種黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ed5f42be75fef36991a1cce8e35119e23fe10a","tid":722573,"uid":22700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T00:50:09.000Z","msg":"如果係sergio ramos 條女會連撚屎都幫佢奶乾淨"},{"pid":"a6330194e8a2a72ace48df0b09ad07b362706c75","tid":722573,"uid":1166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T01:09:14.000Z","msg":"叫親拉莫斯都係狗"},{"pid":"3e2955d4115ba1508b93140444d542d04871e107","tid":722573,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T06:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}